*&quot;Japanese-English dictionary&quot;.1881-1892. 3 vols. by Hoffmann, J. J.
*Japanese-English dictionary by the late Prof. Dr. J. J. Hoffmann, Volumes 1-3 (published posthumously in 1881)</text><links>
